server.commands

Interface Command

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcceptTradeCommand, BuildCityCommand, BuildRoadCommand, BuildSettlementCommand, BuyDevCardCommand, ChangeLogLevelCommand, CommandsCommand, CreateCommand, DiscardCardsCommand, FinishTurnCommand, JoinCommand, ListCommand, LoadCommand, LoginCommand, MaritimeTradeCommand, ModelCommand, MonopolyCardCommand, MonumentCardCommand, OfferTradeCommand, RegisterCommand, ResetCommand, RoadBuildingCardCommand, RobPlayerCommand, RollNumberCommand, SaveCommand, SendChatCommand, SoldierCardCommand, YearOfPlentyCommand

    public interface Command
    Interface for a Command. Contains only one method, which executes the required action. A Command will be called in response to a request sent by a client. Created by benja_000 on 3/13/2015.
